My friends Beni is rope artist, 
we usually talking about alot of ideas of her shibari art, until I met her my images of shibari was very under ground cultureI and felt it had a strong sexual image more than positive energy.

But I've been listening her passion of shibari,
and I felt a new possibility.
I started have interested in design of each space created between ropes.

At this time, We decided to create a design that gives a sense of speed.
We are trying to mix tradition and new things.
I want to elevate her shibari art in to fashion🩶
Let's do alot of new things together @beni.peonia

and please enjoy our styling that leather items and mens fashion with shibari!
Can't wait to share works more🐉
